    {
        "content": "<p>I mean, we do have <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Topology/Order/UpperLowerSetTopology.html#Topology.WithUpperSet.toUpperSet_specializes_toUpperSet\">Topology.WithUpperSet.toUpperSet_specializes_toUpperSet</a></p>",
